$WmMPID_フランネル,ch05_50_Flannel_M_Normal,Face|I'm Keaton. I'm from a race called the
wolfskin.$k$p$Sbs1000|

$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face_Anger|Son.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|Hello, Father.$k$p$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face_Anger|This isn't a social call, Alfonse. I am
on my way to a conference with my
knights.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|I understand. If you have no
objection, however, I'd gladly guard
you till you join up with the army.$k$p$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face_Anger|There is no need. Am I so infirm that
I must lean on my son's arm?$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face_Pain|M-my apologies.$k$p$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face_Anger|*sigh*$k$p$EFace|Do you remember this, Alfonse?$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|A dead branch? It looks quite old...$k$pNo, I don't remember it.$k$p$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face|I see. Well, never mind.$k$p$EFace_Anger|Do not concern yourself over me.
I will rendezvous with my forces.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|Father, wait. Please. Let me—$k$p$WmMPID_グスタフ,ch00_13_Gustaf_M_Normal,Face_Anger|I told you, boy. There is no need.
Worry about your own skin.$k$p$WmMPID_アルフォンス,ch00_01_Alfons_M_Normal,Face|My apologies. Again.$k$pWhat was that branch, I wonder?$k$p$Sbs150|
